### Get all restaurants
GET http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants

### Get a specific restaurant by ID (replace :id with an actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/:id

### Update a restaurant (replace :id with an actual ID)
PATCH http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minimumPurchase": 20,
  "deliveryRadius": 7,
  "tags": ["french", "bistro", "gourmet", "lunch"],
  "planning": {
    "fridayOpen": "10:00",
    "fridayClose": "23:30",
    "saturdayOpen": "10:00",
    "saturdayClose": "23:30"
  }
}

### Delete a restaurant (replace :id with an actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/restaurants/:id
